Lawrence Screw Products Inc. Recognized by Eaton with a Premier Supplier Award for 2015. 

 
Chicago… Our Commodity Manager from Eaton Corporation Isa Stenson visited the Harwood Heights Headquarters to present an Eaton Premier Supplier Award for 2015. We extend a "Thank You" to Isa and all of the decisionmakers at Eaton that helped us to receive this award.
The employees of Lawrence Screw Products are honored to have received the Eaton Premier Award for 2015. Each and every employee at Lawrence Screw plays a unique and important role. Congratulations to all of the employees.Lawrence Screw Products was founded in 1977 and since then has grown to be a world class supplier and specialist in vendor managed inventory and product procurement.Lawrence Screw Products is celebrating 38 years in the business of supporting our customers and helping them to achieve success.. Here at Lawrence Screw Products, Inc. it remains that:
“Customer Service is our most important product” Howard Levinson39+ Years and counting..............

Lawrence Screw Products is a global supplier of fasteners and hardware to Original Equipment Manufacturers. Lawrence Screw provides integrated systems and solutions for procurement and vendor managed inventory allowing our customers to concentrate on what they do best.
Eaton is a global technology leader in power management solutions that make electrical, hydraulic and mechanical power operate more efficiently, reliably, safely and sustainably.

For more information, visit www.eaton.com.
 
 









